All garbage should be placed in the your bins and should be at the location stated in your account. Garbage should be placed in a safe environment as to not cause harm to people on the road.
Main offices are located at the UW Parkside campus in the computer science lab. Our hours are 8:00 a.m to 4:00pm
Bills should be paid by the last day of the month at the main offices either in cash or car
You can change your account info in the your settings page in the app
You can file your complaint in the app in your notifications page
If your pickup date falls on a holiday(ex:Christmas,fourth of july) the pick up date will be moved the day next day
All bins should be the standard size for a garbage bin
Bigger items such as tables or mattresses must first be reported to the main offices or they will not be picked up
There is no maximum number of bins but there will be a bigger charge as you get add more bins into your account
